Feature: Crucio (Cruciatus Curse)

    Inflicts unbearable pain on the recipient of the curse.[HP4] One of the
    three Unforgivable Curses.

    Pronunciation:
        /ˈkruːsi.oʊ/ KREW-see-oh
    Seen/mentioned:
        First seen in Goblet of Fire introduced by Barty Crouch Jr. (acting as
        Moody) and used on a spider. Used regularly by the Death Eaters as
        torture, and by Voldemort as punishment, even against his servants.
